io.github.martindes01.pickcard

Enum Rank

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Rank>
      • io.github.martindes01.pickcard.Rank
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Rank>

    public enum Rank
extends java.lang.Enum<Rank>
    Rank is the public enumeration of card ranks.

    Each enum constant encapsulates two fields.
    The String name is returned using toString().
    The int value is returned using getValue().

    The available enum constants are:

    • TWO
    • THREE
    • FOUR
    • FIVE
    • SIX
    • SEVEN
    • EIGHT
    • NINE
    • TEN
    • JACK
    • QUEEN
    • KING
    • ACE

    1.0
